<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Tutionwala</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
      }
      .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">Welcome to Tutionwala!</div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= username %>,</p>
        <p>A warm welcome to Tutionwala! We’re excited to have you with us.</p>
        <p>
          Your registration is successful, and you’re now part of our learning
          community.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you ever need any help, don’t hesitate to reach out. We’re here to
          support you.
        </p>
        <p><a href="https://tutionwala.com" class="button">Get Started</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Happy Learning!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><strong>Team Tutionwala</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
